rows.label: qst105607_msg0001
rows.name:
So there was a room like this...
Now, to find those records.

rows.label: qst105607_msg0002
rows.name:
Hmmm, where is it? It's
so dusty in here...

rows.label: qst105607_msg0003
rows.name: That's not it... It's an old law book.

rows.label: qst105607_msg0004
rows.name:
Aww! It's a portrait of the Prince
when he was little! So cute~!

rows.label: qst105607_msg0005
rows.name:
What are you findin'?! And don't
leave stuff like this lyin' around!!

rows.label: qst105607_msg0007
rows.name:
There was no book that
looked like it...

rows.label: qst105607_msg0008
rows.name: The King wouldn't lie to us, would he?

rows.label: qst105607_msg0009
rows.name:
Well, he did tell the big lie
about being Adel's descendant.

rows.label: qst105607_msg0010
rows.name: Now's not the time for that!

rows.label: qst105607_msg0011
rows.name:
Just kiddin'... For now, let's report
to my old man. Let's go back up.
